    <li><a href="/examples/">Examples</a>: end-to-end runnable programs across physics, aerospace, medicine, and foundations.</li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/deepcausality-rs/deep_causality/blob/main/papers/effect_propagation_process/epp.pdf">Monograph</a>: the EPP preprint and companion volumes that ground the formal theory.</li>
